# Origin Physical AI — secrets live in PER-APP .env.local (gitignored), not here at the root.
# Each app/service has its own .env.example with the variables it needs:
#   apps/origin-web/.env.example      apps/janus/.env.example
#   services/cobra/.env(.example)      services/chronos/...      services/factoryceo-trm/...
# Copy the relevant one to `.env.local` (or `.env`) in that folder and fill in real values.
#
# NEVER commit a real .env.local. Keep SNAPLII_LIVE=0 unless doing a controlled, owner-run charge.
